They make for
quite an entertaining pot-boiler.

00:30:55.193 --> 00:30:55.985
Really!

00:30:57.318 --> 00:30:59.193
Let's hear it.

00:30:59.985 --> 00:31:05.026
The story begins
with Darpa Narayan Chowdhury.

00:31:05.068 --> 00:31:06.985
I think Sudhir was talking about him.

00:31:07.026 --> 00:31:07.693
Yes.

00:31:07.735 --> 00:31:10.776
Having impressed an Englishman,
he had just received the title of "Raibahadur".

00:31:10.985 --> 00:31:13.151
It was the festive season.

00:31:13.151 --> 00:31:13.693
Okay.

00:31:13.818 --> 00:31:15.068
