because the birds have eaten all the grains.

00:31:35.901 --> 00:31:36.443
Oh.

00:31:36.568 --> 00:31:37.193
Huh?

00:31:37.318 --> 00:31:38.151
Are you serious?

00:31:39.151 --> 00:31:41.318
In that case, who will pay
the government their dues?

00:31:41.318 --> 00:31:42.693
My forefathers?

00:31:43.735 --> 00:31:48.443
- Keeping taxes due is not a good deed...
- No...

00:31:48.443 --> 00:31:50.401
Stop the drums!

00:31:50.401 --> 00:31:51.693
Stop it now!

00:31:51.943 --> 00:31:54.318
