how will the taxes be paid?

00:31:54.401 --> 00:31:55.651
Bishe!

00:31:56.193 --> 00:31:58.651
Get the carriage ready.
Get it ready!

00:31:59.193 --> 00:32:01.193
Bunch of scoundrels!

00:32:02.110 --> 00:32:05.110
Let me get back from the village.
You'll be fired then.

00:32:05.360 --> 00:32:08.068
- You rascal, get the carriage out!
- Get it ready!

00:32:09.235 --> 00:32:11.151
Will I reach tomorrow?

00:32:11.151 --> 00:32:12.068
Yes, Master.

00:32:12.360 --> 00:32:15.443
The carriage will take you to the village
and then you can take a palanquin.

00:32:32.693 --> 00:32:33.943
Why did you stop?

00:32:33.943 --> 00:32:36.276
We have to cross this dangerous forest
by evening.

00:32:36.276 --> 00:32:37.693
Why's everyone silent?

00:32:37.693 --> 00:32:40.401
All of you have to visit the loo together?
Let's get going.

00:32:40.568 --> 00:32:41.526
You'll get a reward--

00:32:43.151 --> 00:32:44.068
Who's there?

00:32:46.901 --> 00:32:48.901
Who are you?
What do you want?

00:32:48.943 --> 00:32:50.860
- They call me the "Noshu" bandit.
- Hmm!

00:32:52.193 --> 00:32:54.068
We are devils personified!

00:32:54.776 --> 00:32:56.943
- Do you know I'm "Raibahadur"?
- We sure do!

00:32:57.193 --> 00:32:59.193
That's why you're loaded!

00:33:00.443 --> 00:33:01.860
Beware!

00:33:01.860 --> 00:33:03.568
Save me, dear Lord!

00:33:03.568 --> 00:33:06.151
Give us everything you have
if you want to save your life.

00:33:06.151 --> 00:33:09.985
Each and every penny, or else...

00:33:10.110 --> 00:33:11.235
Please let me go.

00:33:11.235 --> 00:33:14.276
There's no point crying.
Hurry up and hand over all you have.

00:33:15.193 --> 00:33:18.068
I think I'm going to faint.
I better flee.

