00:35:22.443 --> 00:35:23.943
at an old cemetary.

00:35:24.235 --> 00:35:34.985
Sir Wilkes Booth recommended him
to a trusted native landlord.

00:35:35.985 --> 00:35:38.776
Excuse me, who is the landlord?

00:35:38.776 --> 00:35:41.526
