00:35:45.610 --> 00:35:47.943
Oh yes. Yes sir.

00:35:48.151 --> 00:35:50.485
I'm so fortunate
that Sir Booth recommended me!

00:35:50.610 --> 00:35:51.651
Come sir, come.

00:35:51.651 --> 00:35:53.693
You're my master,
I'm your servant.

00:35:53.735 --> 00:35:56.235
Booth sir calls me Darpa.

00:35:56.443 --> 00:35:57.610
"Darpok",
meaning coward?

00:35:57.735 --> 00:35:58.943
No, no. Darpa, sir.

00:35:58.985 --> 00:36:01.068
Oh, Darpa.
Like Firpo?

00:36:01.235 --> 00:36:04.360
- What does that mean?
- Darpa as in obedient, sir.

00:36:04.735 --> 00:36:05.693
Darpa Narayan Chowdhury...

00:36:05.693 --> 00:36:08.735
- Your most obedient servant, sir.
- Oh, I see.

00:36:08.735 --> 00:36:10.568
Come, sir.
Come in.

00:36:10.860 --> 00:36:14.526
Ramsay was welcomed
with great cordiality by Darpa Narayan Chowdhury.

00:36:14.526 --> 00:36:16.110
Now let's come to the Forties.

00:36:16.110 --> 00:36:17.068
Alright.

00:36:17.776 --> 00:36:23.901
Keshab Narayan Chowdhury was the black sheep
of the Chowdhury family...

00:36:24.235 --> 00:36:27.860
Wine, women, races, gambling...
He had done it all.

00:36:28.193 --> 00:36:32.110
