Good!

00:41:32.610 --> 00:41:36.526
That means my story has managed
to excite your grey cells.

00:41:36.776 --> 00:41:38.235
Now, cut to Calcutta
in the Seventies.

00:41:39.526 --> 00:41:40.401
Those were times
of unrest.

00:41:42.360 --> 00:41:45.026
Radio Peking announced the
thunderous roar of the youth.

00:41:46.068 --> 00:41:49.276
A time when young men were being
indiscriminately killed the police.

00:41:56.943 --> 00:41:57.985
This...

00:41:57.985 --> 00:41:59.610
we'll capture
