01:16:41.594 --> 01:16:45.344
Better not mess with me
Or else, there will be trouble

01:16:45.344 --> 01:16:49.053
My hometown is Darbhanga
I feel more alive after dying

01:16:49.053 --> 01:16:52.678
Everything's on the move

01:16:52.678 --> 01:17:02.386
When all of us start dancing together
We get the whole world moving

01:17:05.344 --> 01:17:12.303
Touchables and untouchables

01:17:12.761 --> 01:17:17.594
There's no difference

01:17:17.594 --> 01:17:21.969
We are just ghosts

01:17:21.969 --> 01:17:27.136
The ghosts of Chowdhury Palace
Ghosts, ghosts, ghosts

01:17:29.386 --> 01:17:34.178
The ghosts of Chowdhury Palace

01:18:04.219 --> 01:18:05.636
That guy is ambidextrous!

01:18:05.636 --> 01:18:08.136
- What?
- Ambidextrous.

01:18:08.136 --> 01:18:13.136
We are the ghosts of Chowdhury Palace

01:18:13.594 --> 01:18:15.428
The event was a grand success.

01:18:15.761 --> 01:18:17.553
Sir Ramsay was overjoyed.

01:18:17.844 --> 01:18:19.886
So much so that he wanted
to entitle everybody "Raibahadur".

01:18:20.428 --> 01:18:23.053
But Darpa Narayan didn't
like the idea much.

01:18:23.053 --> 01:18:28.719
He settled for a picnic the following Sunday
to keep the festive spirit alive.

01:18:29.094 --> 01:18:32.344
So far so good.
But there's something odd...

01:18:32.344 --> 01:18:34.719
Highly suspicious!

01:18:34.803 --> 01:18:38.303
How come Biplab isn't present
in any of these events?

01:18:38.803 --> 01:18:41.053
Patience, my friend.

01:18:41.719 --> 01:18:47.219
Ages may pass before "biplab",
meaning revolution comes!

01:18:48.094 --> 01:18:49.928
Anyway...
What was I saying?

01:18:49.928 --> 01:18:53.344
Yes, the picnic.
A picnic for ghosts!

01:19:04.178 --> 01:19:09.636
(radio playing)

01:19:10.219 --> 01:19:13.303
Here you go, ma'am.

01:19:17.428 --> 01:19:22.011
- Sir?
- Hmm? Thank you. Cheers!

01:19:22.928 --> 01:19:25.344
- Sir.
- Hmm.

01:19:26.053 --> 01:19:27.511
-Sir?
-Hmm.

01:19:27.636 --> 01:19:29.719
That's my point.

01:19:31.011 --> 01:19:32.178
You're cheating!

01:19:32.178 --> 01:19:33.761
-Cheers!
-It's not cheating at all!

01:19:33.761 --> 01:19:36.053
Hey! Come here.

01:19:42.219 --> 01:19:43.178
- Watch out!
- Sorry!

01:19:43.178 --> 01:19:45.469
Let's end the game here,
at love all.

01:19:45.469 --> 01:19:47.386
Please...
Don't even mention the word love.

01:19:47.386 --> 01:19:49.678
You're the most unromantic
person I've met.

01:19:49.886 --> 01:19:53.219
(singing)

01:19:55.928 --> 01:19:59.428
Who's disturbing me
in the middle of a picnic?

01:20:02.761 --> 01:20:04.178
My God!

01:20:04.178 --> 01:20:07.886
Girls always want things to be lovey-dovey.
God, it's a disease!

01:20:07.928 --> 01:20:10.719
Why do you hate girls so much?

01:20:11.303 --> 01:20:13.053
Did anyone dump you?

01:20:13.344 --> 01:20:15.178
Quite a few!

01:20:16.594 --> 01:20:18.261
All girls are not the same.

01:20:19.053 --> 01:20:20.344
I can see that.

01:20:20.844 --> 01:20:26.886
You killed yourself for a guy
instead of looking for him, you're hitting on me!

01:20:30.511 --> 01:20:32.261
What a hassle!

01:20:32.261 --> 01:20:33.844
What's wrong?

01:20:34.678 --> 01:20:35.761
What's wrong?

01:20:36.219 --> 01:20:42.136
I found out that Sam got 10 lakhs
from Dad and took off to Australia.

01:20:42.261 --> 01:20:47.136
And guess what?
He's found himself a rich, foreign chick there!

01:20:48.719 --> 01:20:49.344
I'm sorry.

01:20:51.219 --> 01:20:55.261
This food is amazing!
Must be the cooking oil.

01:20:56.511 --> 01:20:59.636
Tell me something...

01:20:59.719 --> 01:21:02.428
Why did you quit cooking?
To become a soldier?

01:21:02.428 --> 01:21:03.761
Get lost!

01:21:03.761 --> 01:21:04.553
Sorry.

01:21:04.594 --> 01:21:10.219
I know I've made fun of you.
But one has to admit...

01:21:11.178 --> 01:21:12.803
You "faak,"
or cook, very well.

01:21:12.803 --> 01:21:15.761
Mind your language, Bhooth Nath!

01:21:16.094 --> 01:21:16.761
Why?

01:21:16.969 --> 01:21:21.969
I was just saying
that he is a brilliant cook.

01:21:22.803 --> 01:21:26.094
Bhaduri, you are quite a foodie.

01:21:26.261 --> 01:21:30.803
I'm from East Bengal.
You bet I'm a foodie!

01:21:30.969 --> 01:21:37.261
If only you had tasted steamed Hilsa fish
from my hometown...

01:21:37.678 --> 01:21:39.261
Hilsa is tasty...

01:21:40.303 --> 01:21:42.428
But it pales in comparison
to prawns.

01:21:42.761 --> 01:21:44.969
- Prawns?
- Definitely.

01:21:45.178 --> 01:21:48.261
Nothing's tastier than prawns cooked
in a delicate coconut cream sauce!

01:21:48.261 --> 01:21:50.928
You're being childish about this.

01:21:52.136 --> 01:21:55.553
Nothing compares to Hilsa fish
from the Padma river.

01:21:55.719 --> 01:21:57.261
What do you know of prawns?

01:21:57.261 --> 01:22:00.511
I understand it better than you!
Prawns are water insects.

01:22:00.553 --> 01:22:02.178
Prawns are insects?

01:22:02.219 --> 01:22:03.469
You are a complete idiot.

01:22:03.803 --> 01:22:05.261
Bloody Bengali from the East!

01:22:05.844 --> 01:22:07.844
Damn you Westerners!

01:22:07.928 --> 01:22:11.636
You guys put more sugar
than salt in your food!

01:22:11.678 --> 01:22:13.386
And you brag
about water insects!

01:22:13.428 --> 01:22:14.928
- Hey! Get lost.
- Huh?

01:22:14.928 --> 01:22:15.844
Get out!

01:22:16.136 --> 01:22:17.094
Get the hell out now!

01:22:17.094 --> 01:22:18.344
I definitely will.

01:22:18.386 --> 01:22:21.844
I've no intention of staying in a place
where my Hilsa fish is insulted.

01:22:21.844 --> 01:22:23.053
Just go.

01:22:23.053 --> 01:22:25.594
Do we really need a regional strife?
East Bengal versus West Bengal?

01:22:25.594 --> 01:22:27.928
Chowdhury Palace is
in big trouble!

01:22:27.928 --> 01:22:28.803
- What's wrong?
- What are you saying?

01:22:28.803 --> 01:22:29.803
Exactly what you're hearing.

01:22:29.886 --> 01:22:33.636
We were able to live there peacefully
because it was disputed.

01:22:33.636 --> 01:22:36.636
Now the legal issues have been resolved
in an out-of-court settlement.

01:22:36.719 --> 01:22:39.844
All the owners are jointly giving it
away to a promoter.

01:22:39.844 --> 01:22:41.261
- What?
- Yes!

01:22:41.261 --> 01:22:43.928
The house will be demolished
to build a mall.

01:22:43.928 --> 01:22:45.969
- What?
- No, it's a different kind of a mall.

01:22:45.969 --> 01:22:47.386
This is a shopping mall.

01:22:47.386 --> 01:22:51.136
Everyone used to taunt me,
calling me a "girl for sale".

01:22:51.136 --> 01:22:52.928
Now it's actually going
to come true!

01:22:53.011 --> 01:22:58.386
They'll get rid of us along with the house.
I'll become a refugee again!

01:22:58.386 --> 01:23:00.803
Kick me out
of my own house!

01:23:00.928 --> 01:23:04.511
Had this been the British period,
I would have hanged this guy to death.

01:23:04.636 --> 01:23:06.553
Who's taking over the place?

01:23:06.553 --> 01:23:08.219
A man called Bhutoria,
meaning ghost-chaser.

01:23:08.219 --> 01:23:10.303
No wonder he's trying
to chase us ghosts away!

01:23:10.344 --> 01:23:11.761
But how did you find out?

01:23:11.761 --> 01:23:14.969
Since the responsibility of the security
of Chowdhury Palace was on me...

01:23:14.969 --> 01:23:18.469
I had set up a surveillance camera.

01:23:18.469 --> 01:23:22.261
I received an MMS alert
some time back.

01:23:22.844 --> 01:23:27.136
Bhutoria and company have gathered
in front of the main gate.

01:23:27.844 --> 01:23:29.553
My God!

01:23:29.553 --> 01:23:31.719
We should get back right now.

01:23:31.886 --> 01:23:34.053
Comrades, let's go.

01:23:36.094 --> 01:23:36.678
Come.

01:23:36.761 --> 01:23:37.511
There! There!

01:23:37.719 --> 01:23:39.136
- Where is the guy?
- Over there.

01:23:39.136 --> 01:23:40.553
He is the bloody promoter.

01:23:40.678 --> 01:23:43.053
He's come prepared
with a lawyer.

01:23:43.136 --> 01:23:45.053
Who is that tiny guy?

01:23:45.094 --> 01:23:46.303
His sidekick.

01:23:46.344 --> 01:23:48.219
We should beat the hell out of them!

01:23:50.803 --> 01:23:53.219
Here you go Bhutoria...
Now it's all yours.

01:23:53.303 --> 01:23:54.344
At last.

01:23:54.511 --> 01:24:01.469
Ganesh Bhutoria always makes sure
that he gets whatever he wants.

01:24:02.636 --> 01:24:06.094
I'll turn this place around!

01:24:06.261 --> 01:24:09.053
There's original Burma Teak here.
You'll get a good price for it.

01:24:09.594 --> 01:24:11.344
That apart, there's...

01:24:11.344 --> 01:24:12.553
What about the brick inside?
Will I get a price for that too?

01:24:12.553 --> 01:24:16.011
No, sir.
The flooring inside is made of Italian marble.

01:24:16.011 --> 01:24:18.136
- Oh.
- Extra profit!

01:24:18.178 --> 01:24:22.136
I'll put it to good use.

01:24:22.636 --> 01:24:24.803
It'll be a superhit!
Go get a coconut.

01:24:25.928 --> 01:24:27.219
Why the hell are you stammering?

01:24:27.219 --> 01:24:30.928
Which coconut, sir?
The one with water or--

01:24:30.928 --> 01:24:32.844
Stop stammering, you fool.

01:24:32.928 --> 01:24:34.344
Doesn't know anything!

01:24:34.594 --> 01:24:38.553
Before any auspicious event, you need
to crack open a coconut.

01:24:38.803 --> 01:24:39.678
That kind of a coconut.

01:24:40.053 --> 01:24:41.719
Do you want me
to crack open your head instead?

01:24:41.719 --> 01:24:44.219
- Sorry, sir.
- Go.

01:24:44.219 --> 01:24:46.053
I'll get it right away!

01:24:46.303 --> 01:24:50.428
Possession is the most important thing.
It's the nine points of law.

01:24:50.928 --> 01:24:52.761
You know...

01:24:52.803 --> 01:24:55.678
I'll make a beautiful shopping mall
on this plot.

01:24:56.094 --> 01:24:58.511
Parking lot in the basement.

01:24:58.636 --> 01:25:00.469
Groceries on the ground floor.

01:25:01.178 --> 01:25:05.553
Level one will have clothing
and lingerie.

01:25:06.803 --> 01:25:10.178
Level two will have jewellery
and fashion accessories.

01:25:10.344 --> 01:25:11.844
Level three will have the food court.

01:25:12.011 --> 01:25:14.178
And level four will be star studded!

01:25:14.261 --> 01:25:19.511
Multiplexes, premiere shows, film stars...
It'll be a five-storey, five-star mall.

01:25:19.594 --> 01:25:22.636
I've even thought of a name...
Five Star Plaza!

01:25:23.428 --> 01:25:26.053
I'll talk to my numerologist
and finalise everything.

01:25:26.053 --> 01:25:31.136
Sir, there's a five-star hotel called
"Sonar Bangla" or The Golden House.

01:25:31.219 --> 01:25:34.719
You should name this "Bhooth Bangla",
or The Haunted House, after yourself!

01:25:35.136 --> 01:25:36.136
Shut up!

01:25:36.261 --> 01:25:37.011
Hail Lord Ganesha!

01:25:37.386 --> 01:25:40.594
The fate of Chowdhury Palace is
in deep despair!

01:25:40.636 --> 01:25:44.011
I'm ready to sacrifice my life again.

01:25:44.094 --> 01:25:46.678
You can't give up your life twice!

01:25:46.678 --> 01:25:49.928
Once it's out of the tube,
you can't squeeze it back in.

01:25:50.969 --> 01:25:53.761
I've asked the architect
to begin work immediately.

01:25:53.761 --> 01:25:56.511
This needs to be transformed
into the best mall in town.

01:25:56.553 --> 01:26:00.636
There'll be a fountain here,
a fibre glass roof on top...

01:26:00.761 --> 01:26:05.094
Bubble lifts, escalator,
central air conditioning...

01:26:05.094 --> 01:26:08.178
It'll be a mini Singapore
in Calcutta!

01:26:08.386 --> 01:26:14.636
You're going to build Singapore here...
Will the municipality just sit and watch?

01:26:14.886 --> 01:26:17.053
Are you from the municipal corporation?

01:26:19.428 --> 01:26:22.303
- We run the entire municipality!
- Oh...

01:26:22.303 --> 01:26:25.969
This is our responsibility
towards society.

01:26:26.219 --> 01:26:28.678
So what do I have to do?

01:26:28.803 --> 01:26:29.886
Pay up.

01:26:30.136 --> 01:26:33.303
Can't let you enjoy it all
by yourself now, can we?

01:26:33.553 --> 01:26:35.094
The revolutionary poet
Kazi Nazrul Islam wrote...

01:26:35.094 --> 01:26:38.178
"Give and take at the same time,
don't walk away from it".

01:26:38.261 --> 01:26:40.678
You'll "give", we'll "take"...

01:26:40.928 --> 01:26:43.178
We'll be in it together.
Or else, I won't go away.

01:26:43.178 --> 01:26:44.553
How much do I have to pay?

01:26:44.594 --> 01:26:46.553
One...hard cash.

01:26:47.428 --> 01:26:49.219
Can't we negotiate?

01:26:49.219 --> 01:26:50.261
Sik-Sik--

01:26:50.261 --> 01:26:51.303
What the hell do you mean, sick?

01:26:51.344 --> 01:26:53.178
Sixty-five thousand?

01:26:54.011 --> 01:26:54.803
What's your name?

01:26:55.219 --> 01:26:58.136
My name...
Gu-Gu-Gu...

01:26:58.386 --> 01:26:59.386
Gu... What?

01:26:59.969 --> 01:27:02.553
My name is T. K. Guchait.

01:27:02.928 --> 01:27:05.594
Do you think I'm a beggar?

01:27:05.636 --> 01:27:07.344
Do you know who I am?

01:27:07.344 --> 01:27:10.803
With a single phone call,
I can start a curfew in town!

01:27:10.844 --> 01:27:13.553
Always remember, I am Pod Podhan.

01:27:13.553 --> 01:27:15.344
Your name is Pod?

01:27:15.344 --> 01:27:18.053
Hey!
Not Pod... It's Promod.

01:27:18.219 --> 01:27:20.344
Oh, Parmod.

01:27:20.886 --> 01:27:22.844
Nice name.

01:27:23.719 --> 01:27:25.261
Don't mess with him.

01:27:25.636 --> 01:27:29.928
I might have a minor speech problem
but I'm quite cultured otherwise.

01:27:29.969 --> 01:27:32.803
In fact, I'd written a poem
in high school.

01:27:32.803 --> 01:27:35.386
"There's tremendous rain,
That's why be patient

01:27:35.386 --> 01:27:38.303
East Bengal has Poshanto,
Mohan Bagan has Poshun"

01:27:38.553 --> 01:27:41.594
- These days, he writes highbred poetry.
- Don't think he is an idiot.

01:27:41.636 --> 01:27:42.094
Not at all...

01:27:42.094 --> 01:27:44.261
He's got the attitude
of a rebel, too.

01:27:44.261 --> 01:27:45.178
His demand must be kept.

01:27:45.178 --> 01:27:47.636
You people cannot
threaten my client like this.

01:27:47.636 --> 01:27:49.094
Shut up!

01:27:49.553 --> 01:27:51.844
You're trying to show off
in that stupid black coat of yours, huh?

01:27:52.261 --> 01:27:55.928
I hang out with your boss from the High Court.
We drink together.

01:27:55.969 --> 01:27:58.594
He's going to receive the ticket
in the next elections, right?

01:27:59.011 --> 01:28:04.303
Hey! I'm being very clear.
One crore, hard cash.

01:28:04.511 --> 01:28:07.594
Otherwise, get lost.

01:28:07.886 --> 01:28:12.053
Please consider my plea, sir.
One crore is a little too much.

01:28:12.053 --> 01:28:14.594
It's not just for myself.

01:28:14.678 --> 01:28:17.178
Different political parties...
The ruling party, the opposition...

01:28:17.178 --> 01:28:18.928
All them them
have a share in it.

01:28:19.053 --> 01:28:20.428
As Tagore wrote...

01:28:20.428 --> 01:28:23.761
"We are there for other's sake
and they are there for ours".

01:28:24.011 --> 01:28:25.511
In other words...

01:28:25.511 --> 01:28:29.803
United we stand,
divided we misunderstand!

01:28:30.303 --> 01:28:33.303
But so much money...
All at one go!

01:28:33.303 --> 01:28:34.594
Take your time.

01:28:34.636 --> 01:28:37.553
I'm giving you seven days.
Get the cash together.

01:28:37.969 --> 01:28:43.178
You can forget about this project
if you don't pay up by then.

01:28:43.303 --> 01:28:47.011
Remember my name.
"Pod Podhan".

01:28:47.469 --> 01:28:48.261
Let's go.

01:28:48.428 --> 01:28:51.386
You better remember his words!

01:28:51.678 --> 01:28:54.011
There's a twist
in the tale.

01:28:54.094 --> 01:28:56.636
Nothing of the sort.
That bloody promoter is filthy rich.

01:28:56.636 --> 01:28:58.344
To him, one crore is dirt!

01:28:58.428 --> 01:29:03.553
He might be rich.
But he'll negotiate till his last breath.

01:29:03.636 --> 01:29:04.969
After all, he's a businessman.

01:29:04.969 --> 01:29:08.178
So, we have some time
and a window of opportunity.

01:29:08.178 --> 01:29:11.386
We can't just sit idle.

01:29:11.844 --> 01:29:14.344
Biplab would have figured
out a guerilla warfare plan.

01:29:14.344 --> 01:29:16.303
Where is he?

01:29:16.303 --> 01:29:18.969
He has a lot of sympathy
for poor people like us.

01:29:19.094 --> 01:29:20.386
He's in South India...

01:29:20.386 --> 01:29:24.303
working with revolutionaries
on improvised explosives.

01:29:24.344 --> 01:29:25.969
But I can fill in for him!

01:29:26.011 --> 01:29:27.011
Listen, son.

01:29:27.094 --> 01:29:31.344
It's very easy to wear a Che Guevara shirt
and talk about a proxy war.

01:29:31.428 --> 01:29:33.719
- You know, in the year--
- Excuse me.

01:29:33.761 --> 01:29:35.011
First of all, this shirt is mine.

01:29:35.094 --> 01:29:39.636
Second, you're mispronouncing the name
of the guy printed on it.

01:29:39.636 --> 01:29:42.636
- And third--
- Friends, let's not fight amonsgt ourselves.

01:29:42.636 --> 01:29:44.469
Now we need a master plan.

01:29:44.511 --> 01:29:47.761
- Let's listen to the army man.
- Thank you, sir.

01:29:47.886 --> 01:29:51.469
In the year 1971,
during the Bangladesh War...

01:29:51.469 --> 01:29:52.719
General Yahia...

01:29:52.719 --> 01:29:55.678
Oh, no, not again!
No more nostalgia.

01:29:55.678 --> 01:29:57.969
Okay, okay.

01:29:58.053 --> 01:30:02.136
In any combat,
the first stage is intelligence gathering.

01:30:02.344 --> 01:30:03.928
Covert survey.

01:30:03.969 --> 01:30:07.761
We have to find out the strengths
and weaknesses of the opponent.

01:30:07.803 --> 01:30:10.636
Then, half the battle is won.

01:30:10.761 --> 01:30:12.844
Oh God, who's going to do that?

01:30:12.844 --> 01:30:16.844
We can't use Khaja for that.

01:30:16.844 --> 01:30:17.553
You fool!

01:30:17.553 --> 01:30:19.219
What?

01:30:19.219 --> 01:30:24.344
I have acted in a few local plays...
with social or historical themes...

01:30:24.511 --> 01:30:27.094
"Really, Seleucus,
what a diverse country!"

01:30:27.178 --> 01:30:28.386
Lucida Grande

01:30:28.386 --> 01:30:29.636
Wait.

01:30:30.094 --> 01:30:32.469
I don't think anybody can act better
than me here.

01:30:32.469 --> 01:30:35.636
All of your talents will be put
to use in good time.

01:30:36.094 --> 01:30:44.594
But at the moment, we need the cooperation
of Lt. Pablo Patranobis and Capt. Koyel Dhar.

01:30:45.219 --> 01:30:47.469
Don't mind my words, young man.

01:30:47.553 --> 01:30:51.136
In times of war, the commander needs
to be harsh when required.

01:30:51.261 --> 01:30:53.136
Okay, Commander.

01:30:53.261 --> 01:30:54.511
What can we do for you?

01:30:54.886 --> 01:30:56.469
Not much...

01:30:56.636 --> 01:30:59.678
You gus are
about to get married.

01:30:59.886 --> 01:31:00.928
- What!
- Huh?

01:31:01.011 --> 01:31:04.678
What you do in reality
is entirely your business.

01:31:04.719 --> 01:31:07.094
You'll go to Bhutoria's office...

01:31:07.094 --> 01:31:11.386
as a soon-to-be-married couple.

01:31:11.386 --> 01:31:16.011
You'll pretend to be looking
for an apartment.

01:31:16.178 --> 01:31:22.844
Your mission is to extract vital information
from Bhutoria's sidekick about his boss.

01:31:22.844 --> 01:31:25.844
Bhutoria treats Guchait really badly.

01:31:25.928 --> 01:31:28.969
That's why, deep inside,
he has a raging anger for his boss.

01:31:28.969 --> 01:31:34.053
Besides, he wears all kinds of rings,
which means he's insecure.

01:31:34.053 --> 01:31:37.511
These weaknesses need
to be exploited to get information.

01:31:38.053 --> 01:31:39.511
We're looking for a nice apartment...

01:31:39.511 --> 01:31:41.428
- Around 800 square feet.
- Yeah.

01:31:41.428 --> 01:31:42.678
In South Calcutta.

01:31:42.761 --> 01:31:44.803
South-facing, with two bedrooms.

01:31:44.928 --> 01:31:49.636
We just saw an advertisement...
Golden Greens.

01:31:49.678 --> 01:31:54.386
If you book now,
you'll get a special rebate.

01:31:54.386 --> 01:31:57.803
Check this out.
Lots of greenery...

01:31:57.803 --> 01:31:59.928
Amazing scenic beauty!

01:32:00.219 --> 01:32:03.344
You can also see this water body
from the balcony.

01:32:03.344 --> 01:32:10.886
Both sides are south-facing.
We also arrange for bank loans.

01:32:11.219 --> 01:32:13.178
Can we see the site sometime?

01:32:13.178 --> 01:32:18.386
Any day.
How about today?

01:32:18.761 --> 01:32:20.803
No, not today.

01:32:21.928 --> 01:32:23.094
It won't take very long.

01:32:23.094 --> 01:32:29.928
We'll also arrange
for a vehicle.

01:32:30.261 --> 01:32:32.678
No, today won't work.

01:32:32.678 --> 01:32:36.594
Today we have
to visit Saint Bhooth Nath.

01:32:36.594 --> 01:32:40.594
He's not available very often, you know.

01:32:40.594 --> 01:32:43.553
Thank God he's here right now.

01:32:43.553 --> 01:32:46.678
He's in Calcutta just
for three days.

01:32:46.678 --> 01:32:52.094
Who is Saint Bhooth Nath?
A famous astrologer?

01:32:52.094 --> 01:32:54.219
- Are you serious?
- Not just an astrologer...

01:32:54.261 --> 01:32:58.344
He has the past, present
and the future at his fingertips!

01:32:58.511 --> 01:33:01.469
Barrack Obama had called for him.
He refused to go.

01:33:01.761 --> 01:33:06.136
He has no interest
in such worldly matters.

01:33:06.136 --> 01:33:07.136
Sir...

01:33:07.136 --> 01:33:13.469
Will you please introuce me
to Saint Bhooth Nath?

01:33:13.469 --> 01:33:16.261
I'm going through
a really bad time.

01:33:16.261 --> 01:33:18.636
There's peace neither at home
nor at office.

01:33:18.636 --> 01:33:25.303
I've tried all the amulets available
for good luck.

01:33:25.303 --> 01:33:27.344
But nothing worked.

01:33:27.344 --> 01:33:31.928
Please see what you can do.

01:33:31.928 --> 01:33:36.678
But the saint does not
meet people easily.

01:33:36.678 --> 01:33:41.928
Ma'am, please do something.
My life has become unbearable.

01:33:41.928 --> 01:33:44.844
I'll end up committing suicide.

01:33:44.844 --> 01:33:46.178
Our group will get stronger!

01:33:46.178 --> 01:33:46.886
Sorry?

01:33:46.886 --> 01:33:50.969
I was just saying
that he can't say no to Koyel.

01:33:50.969 --> 01:33:54.803
Ma'am, please help me.

01:33:54.803 --> 01:33:58.636
I'll get you the apartment
at a minium rate.

01:33:59.386 --> 01:34:03.886
Since you're insisting...

01:34:03.886 --> 01:34:09.178
But if you bring up money,
he will get very angry.

01:34:10.136 --> 01:34:10.928
Praise the Lord!

01:34:10.928 --> 01:34:18.636
(chanting)

01:34:18.636 --> 01:34:22.053
I had spoken to you
about him.

01:34:22.053 --> 01:34:25.011
He's in great distress.
Please help him.

01:34:25.011 --> 01:34:28.178
Full moon, half moon, solutions and problems!
(speaks gibberish)

01:34:28.178 --> 01:34:31.344
Sir, have mercy on me.

01:34:31.344 --> 01:34:32.844
Women and wealth, digestives or not...
(continues gbberish)

01:34:32.844 --> 01:34:35.219
Your life and death
are now in my hands.

01:34:35.219 --> 01:34:36.969
Let me hear
about your troubles.

01:34:36.969 --> 01:34:39.553
- My trouble is my boss.
- Boss?

01:34:39.553 --> 01:34:45.928
He is always humiliating me.

01:34:45.928 --> 01:34:49.053
We have fix him, right?

01:34:49.053 --> 01:34:54.428
He's really wicked.

01:34:54.428 --> 01:34:56.636
He needs to be taught a lesson.

01:34:56.636 --> 01:34:59.886
Is that so?
Let's hear about his deeds.

01:34:59.928 --> 01:35:01.969
He has committed horrible crimes.

01:35:01.969 --> 01:35:07.053
He even burnt his wife
to death!

01:35:07.678 --> 01:35:11.928
She lived up
to her name, Laxmi.

01:35:11.928 --> 01:35:14.678
Really?

01:35:14.886 --> 01:35:19.636
After getting information
about Bhutoria's past...

01:35:19.636 --> 01:35:21.678
The master plan was drawn up.

01:35:21.678 --> 01:35:26.136
Unfortunately, people aren't scared
of ghosts like they used to be.

01:35:26.136 --> 01:35:28.969
They would have to catch
people alone at night.

01:35:28.969 --> 01:35:30.969
They would have to catch
people alone at night.

01:35:31.136 --> 01:35:32.178
They were all very charged up!

01:35:32.386 --> 01:35:35.303
The most vital thing now
is finding contacts.

01:35:35.303 --> 01:35:38.886
There's a social networking site
for ghosts, Spookbook!

01:35:38.886 --> 01:35:41.761
- We can get contacts from there.
- Spookbook!

01:35:42.886 --> 01:35:44.136
There's really a website
like that?

01:35:44.136 --> 01:35:46.886
- Yes.
- Its slogan is "the real friend of a ghost".

01:35:46.886 --> 01:35:47.844
Good.

01:35:47.844 --> 01:35:50.011
Let's see
if we can find a volunteer.

01:35:50.261 --> 01:35:52.678
They found exactly
what they were looking for.

01:35:52.678 --> 01:35:54.136
One-armed Kartik...

01:35:54.261 --> 01:35:55.719
a terror in his locality.

01:35:55.719 --> 01:36:01.761
He was a thug
for political parties.

01:36:01.761 --> 01:36:05.511
He lost his arm
while making a crude bomb.

01:36:05.553 --> 01:36:07.553
But that didn't curb his spirit.

01:36:07.553 --> 01:36:12.761
He recently got bumped off
by a member of a rival group.

01:36:17.636 --> 01:36:21.303
I'll have to put this here.
It's hurting me in the wrong place.

01:36:21.428 --> 01:36:22.678
Whom do I have to
get ride of?

01:36:22.678 --> 01:36:24.844
Fifty percent before the job
and fifty after the job.

01:36:24.844 --> 01:36:26.636
Kartik dear...

01:36:26.636 --> 01:36:28.886
We have risen
above violence.

01:36:28.886 --> 01:36:31.969
We are in great trouble.
Help us out.

01:36:31.969 --> 01:36:35.178
Want to throw out the tenants?
No problem. I have my ways.

01:36:35.428 --> 01:36:38.761
No, we haven't called you
to torture anyone.

01:36:38.761 --> 01:36:41.469
We have called you
to save us from torture.

01:36:41.469 --> 01:36:45.678
You'll be rewarded for this.

01:36:45.678 --> 01:36:46.928
Who's this cartoon?

01:36:46.928 --> 01:36:49.428
Is he from a theatre group
or something?

01:36:49.428 --> 01:36:53.136
Kartik, please...
We are in great trouble.

01:36:53.344 --> 01:36:54.719
Okay, fine.

01:36:54.719 --> 01:36:56.053
I can't turn down
a girl's request.

01:36:56.303 --> 01:36:59.136
You will be blessed.
Khaja Khan is right.

01:36:59.136 --> 01:37:01.261
So many helpless ghosts...
Where do we take shelter?

01:37:01.511 --> 01:37:02.969
Blessed?

01:37:03.053 --> 01:37:06.344
I'm almost drowning in sin.

01:37:06.428 --> 01:37:08.428
The world is full
of traitors.

01:37:09.011 --> 01:37:12.136
I taught that kid
how to use a knife.

01:37:12.428 --> 01:37:15.594
I had no clue
when he turned on me.

01:37:15.594 --> 01:37:18.511
So I went when he called for me
but he slit his own mentor's throat!

01:37:18.844 --> 01:37:21.719
I'll honour you
with the Queen's Cross.

01:37:21.761 --> 01:37:24.178
Who the hell are you?
Really, you are a weird bunch!

01:37:24.386 --> 01:37:27.136
You just have to help us.

01:37:27.136 --> 01:37:30.719
Okay, fine.
Like I said, I can't turn a lady down.

01:37:30.719 --> 01:37:34.344
I always used to get my girl
whatever she wanted.

01:37:34.344 --> 01:37:40.928
Everything, down to those
tight, low-waist jeans!

01:37:40.928 --> 01:37:43.553
There's just one problem.
Everyone knows that you are dead.

01:37:43.553 --> 01:37:44.761
Not at all!

01:37:44.969 --> 01:37:48.011
Those jerks had hidden my body
in a septic tank.

01:37:48.011 --> 01:37:50.053
Nobody knows
that I am dead.

01:37:50.053 --> 01:37:52.594
Everybody thinks
that I've gone underground!

01:37:52.594 --> 01:37:54.594
Good, you won't be suspected.

01:37:54.594 --> 01:37:56.303
Just tell me
what I have to do.

01:37:56.303 --> 01:37:58.136
You have to go
to Bhutoria's office.

01:37:58.136 --> 01:37:58.803
Tomorrow.

01:37:58.803 --> 01:38:00.386
Bhutoria?
Is he a ghost too?

01:38:00.386 --> 01:38:01.178
No.

01:38:01.386 --> 01:38:03.928
A promoter.
The owner of Magic Realty.

01:38:04.094 --> 01:38:04.886
Hello?

01:38:05.303 --> 01:38:07.094
I'm speaking on behalf
of Magic Realty.

01:38:07.594 --> 01:38:10.511
Our office staff is facing issues
with their hard disks.

01:38:11.011 --> 01:38:12.803
No, we are unable
to save our files.

01:38:13.303 --> 01:38:14.803
Boss has already asked twice!

01:38:15.178 --> 01:38:16.511
But it's written
in the contract.

01:38:17.094 --> 01:38:18.803
My God, what's wrong
with this man?

01:38:18.928 --> 01:38:21.928
Please send someone immediately.

01:38:22.803 --> 01:38:23.344
How strange...

01:38:23.386 --> 01:38:26.428
Hi, babe,
I need to meet your boss.

01:38:26.636 --> 01:38:28.094
Where are you from?

01:38:28.094 --> 01:38:29.594
From far, far away.

01:38:29.636 --> 01:38:31.469
Sir's in a meeting.

01:38:31.469 --> 01:38:32.594
Can I take a message?

01:38:32.636 --> 01:38:35.928
Whether you give your boss a message
or a kiss, is your call.

01:38:36.094 --> 01:38:37.511
I have urgent business
wth him.

01:38:37.511 --> 01:38:39.261
I just told you...
Sir is busy.

01:38:39.261 --> 01:38:41.636
I don't care.
Tell him it's urgent.

01:38:41.636 --> 01:38:42.303
Wait.

01:38:42.303 --> 01:38:44.428
Hello?
Mr. Guchait, come here right now!

01:38:44.428 --> 01:38:45.803
I don't have time to waste.

01:38:49.303 --> 01:38:50.928
What's wrong?

01:38:51.261 --> 01:38:54.386
He wants to meet sir urgently.

01:38:55.803 --> 01:38:58.011
- Bhuto-Bhuto--
- Who's Bhuto, huh?

01:38:58.261 --> 01:39:00.219
Bhuto-Bhutoria is busy.

01:39:00.344 --> 01:39:01.678
Why don't you tell me?

01:39:01.678 --> 01:39:03.261
Who are you, Johny?

01:39:03.261 --> 01:39:06.053
I am T-T-T. K. Guchait.

01:39:06.053 --> 01:39:08.678
You'll stop stammering
when you get punched in the nose!

01:39:09.303 --> 01:39:10.386
Finalise it at 25 lakhs.

01:39:10.386 --> 01:39:11.303
Hey, Bhuto!

01:39:11.303 --> 01:39:12.094
Yeah.

01:39:12.636 --> 01:39:13.344
Who is it?

01:39:13.678 --> 01:39:14.636
Kartik.

01:39:15.803 --> 01:39:17.136
It's important.

01:39:17.136 --> 01:39:18.928
The problem is yours,
the solution is mine.

01:39:18.928 --> 01:39:21.261
If you don't hear me out, it's your loss.
If you do, you profit.

01:39:21.511 --> 01:39:22.511
Profit?

01:39:23.303 --> 01:39:24.636
- Sit.
- Thank you.

01:39:25.428 --> 01:39:27.053
What a coincidence!

01:39:27.053 --> 01:39:31.969
Your name is Kartik
and my name is Ganesh.

01:39:32.053 --> 01:39:34.428
Ganesh Bhutoria.

01:39:34.719 --> 01:39:39.303
We are like the mythological brothers
Kartik and Ganesh.

01:39:39.553 --> 01:39:40.011
Yes?

01:39:40.011 --> 01:39:42.844
This guy is dangerous, sir.

01:39:42.844 --> 01:39:44.053
Okay, okay.

01:39:44.511 --> 01:39:45.511
What?

01:39:45.636 --> 01:39:47.886
Did you get my character certficate?

01:39:47.886 --> 01:39:49.469
You're famous!

01:39:49.469 --> 01:39:51.386
You mean infamous.

01:39:52.094 --> 01:39:53.969
Everybody is scared
of one-armed Kartik.

01:39:54.636 --> 01:39:57.344
My hand got drilled
while trying to dodge a bullet.

01:39:57.386 --> 01:39:59.594
I used to measure my targets
through the hole.

01:39:59.761 --> 01:40:01.928
People started calling me
the "Hole Master".

01:40:02.261 --> 01:40:04.928
And then I lost
my entire hand.

01:40:05.511 --> 01:40:07.636
From the "Hole Master"
to "One-armed Kartik"!

01:40:08.344 --> 01:40:12.594
Tell me what I can do for you.

01:40:12.678 --> 01:40:14.511
I'll be the one
doing things for you!

01:40:14.594 --> 01:40:16.719
But not for free.
It'll be a give and take.

01:40:17.553 --> 01:40:18.594
What do you mean?

01:40:20.469 --> 01:40:23.261
How much has Promod Prodhan asked for?

01:40:23.969 --> 01:40:26.303
How do you know
that he has asked for money?

01:40:26.303 --> 01:40:28.553
Let me guess,
One... right?

01:40:28.636 --> 01:40:31.094
One... as in?

01:40:31.594 --> 01:40:36.636
Why are you playing dumb, man?

01:40:36.636 --> 01:40:38.178
What do you want?

01:40:38.178 --> 01:40:41.386
Cut the crap...
I can make the settlement at 50 lakhs.

01:40:41.386 --> 01:40:42.844
I will keep four percent.

01:40:42.844 --> 01:40:45.386
You will be saving 48 lakhs.

01:40:45.386 --> 01:40:46.719
Really?

01:40:47.511 --> 01:40:51.428
One-armed Kartik never goes back
on his word.

01:40:51.719 --> 01:40:57.136
My political connections are very high.
I know Promod Prodhan's father too.

01:40:57.136 --> 01:40:59.719
You know his father too?

01:40:59.719 --> 01:41:01.719
- Not his real father.
- Oh.

01:41:02.219 --> 01:41:04.094
His godfather...
D. N. Chowdhury.

01:41:04.219 --> 01:41:06.761
He's a real big shot!

01:41:07.261 --> 01:41:09.719
You saved me, Kartik.
Thank you.

01:41:10.011 --> 01:41:11.344
Mention not!

01:41:11.969 --> 01:41:15.011
Make sure you're at Chowdhury Palace
with 50 lakhs.

01:41:15.136 --> 01:41:16.719
At 10 o'clock.

01:41:17.011 --> 01:41:20.094
If you are lucky,
you might meet some rich, foreign clients.

01:41:20.178 --> 01:41:22.469
Rich, foreign clients?

01:41:22.469 --> 01:41:23.928
Wipes his a**
on dollar bills!

01:41:24.594 --> 01:41:25.969
They want to invest here.

01:41:25.969 --> 01:41:28.303
My God!
Foreign investors?

01:41:28.303 --> 01:41:31.511
Do you think I'm a
small-time guy?

01:41:32.178 --> 01:41:32.928
Okay.

01:41:33.428 --> 01:41:36.094
I'll leave in the morning
right after the religious cereremony.

01:41:36.094 --> 01:41:36.886
By 10 o'clock.

01:41:36.886 --> 01:41:38.636
Not in the morning.

01:41:38.761 --> 01:41:40.136
Such deals can't be done
in the day time!

01:41:40.136 --> 01:41:41.803
I meant 10 o'clock at night.

01:41:41.803 --> 01:41:43.553
Make sure you're alone.
And bring the money.

01:41:43.553 --> 01:41:46.844
Your sidekicks won't be allowed in.
The whole deal will be confidential.

01:41:47.136 --> 01:41:48.053
All alone?

01:41:48.469 --> 01:41:49.969
I mean, my chauffeur will be there.

01:41:49.969 --> 01:41:52.136
You might be followed
if you come in your car.

01:41:52.219 --> 01:41:53.928
I'll send you a rickshaw.

01:41:53.969 --> 01:41:55.886
I'll have to go in a rickshaw?
Won't it be risky?

01:41:55.886 --> 01:41:57.219
You'll be carrying
a lot of money.

01:41:57.386 --> 01:41:59.386
With Atmaram around,
there'll be nothing to worry about.

01:41:59.803 --> 01:42:00.719
Atmaram?

01:42:00.719 --> 01:42:01.803
The rickshaw puller.

01:42:02.011 --> 01:42:03.594
Trustworthy man.

01:42:03.678 --> 01:42:05.886
He'll make sure you reach safely.

01:42:09.636 --> 01:42:11.678
He's here.
Very good.

01:42:11.678 --> 01:42:12.678
It's all set.

01:42:12.761 --> 01:42:13.469
D. N. Chowdhury?

01:42:13.469 --> 01:42:15.219
Everything's ready as planned.
He's upstairs.

01:42:15.219 --> 01:42:15.928
Come.

01:42:15.928 --> 01:42:18.136
- Got the cash?
- All of it.

01:42:18.136 --> 01:42:19.136
And the foreign client?

01:42:19.136 --> 01:42:20.553
Everyone's here.

01:42:20.636 --> 01:42:24.094
- I've arranged for some entertainment.
- That's great!

01:42:24.094 --> 01:42:28.803
And Bengalis celebrate so many festivals!

01:42:29.011 --> 01:42:30.136
Should I take off my shoes?

01:42:30.136 --> 01:42:31.719
There are different ways of doing things here.
Just come along.

01:42:31.719 --> 01:42:32.928
Okay.

01:42:34.636 --> 01:42:36.719
(song playing)

01:42:36.719 --> 01:42:37.553
Come, come.

01:42:40.053 --> 01:42:40.886
Wow!

01:42:41.178 --> 01:42:42.844
Is this a business meeting
or a party?

01:42:43.094 --> 01:42:46.344
They are all VIPs.
We have to entertain them.

01:42:46.344 --> 01:42:49.636
Meet D. N. Chowdhury.

01:42:49.636 --> 01:42:51.594
And you are?
Go on.

01:42:51.969 --> 01:42:53.678
Sir Richmond, from London.

01:42:53.678 --> 01:42:55.803
Hello.
Please be seated.

01:42:56.844 --> 01:42:57.928
Have a drink.

01:42:57.928 --> 01:42:58.678
Sir?

01:42:58.761 --> 01:42:59.428
Alcohol?

01:42:59.511 --> 01:43:01.594
Foreign liquor!
Tell me what you'll have.

01:43:02.136 --> 01:43:04.178
I don't drink.

01:43:04.178 --> 01:43:06.803
Is he serious?

01:43:07.553 --> 01:43:10.053
And to think
I made so many arrangements.

01:43:10.844 --> 01:43:13.219
Sir, what is the name
of your company?

01:43:13.678 --> 01:43:15.386
East India Company.

01:43:15.469 --> 01:43:17.053
East India Company.

01:43:17.053 --> 01:43:18.178
Indian company?

01:43:18.469 --> 01:43:19.969
Famous company.

01:43:20.136 --> 01:43:21.969
It's bought over
almost the entire country!

01:43:22.553 --> 01:43:24.719
How much are you paying
for this house?

01:43:25.011 --> 01:43:27.053
About 10 crores.

01:43:28.053 --> 01:43:30.219
My entire land would be worth...

01:43:30.219 --> 01:43:32.553
- about five thousand--
- Crores!

01:43:32.928 --> 01:43:34.219
Five thousand crores!

01:43:34.219 --> 01:43:35.678
- Right?
- Yes, yes.

01:43:36.053 --> 01:43:37.094
Land?

01:43:37.094 --> 01:43:40.428
Tea estate.
Big shot!

01:43:42.469 --> 01:43:45.636
So, you don't like alcohol.
But you like chicks I hope.

01:43:45.844 --> 01:43:47.053
Chicks?

